{"tid":203010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"釣魚友：入黎一齊分享下心得","createTime":"2017-04-16T03:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T19:06:01.000Z","uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b58625ff4ca535b291c8cdf2c373d0d28e177c2","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"連登巴打絲打們有冇人釣開魚<br />\n<br />\n分享下去邊釣開魚，同艇釣定岸釣？<br />\n入黎分享下"},{"pid":"3287d040f6ffa266bf0ec0b8fbfd20c676d170eb","tid":203010,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"db1009df484161905a010a7aac115765c0d42bc9","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:48:58.000Z","msg":"我講先<br />\n<br />\n去開油塘，將軍澳<br />\n<br />\n有岸釣同艇釣<br />\n中細魚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f441bcd6dae29b93cbffa7fc387c07a6b3dceb4","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"（新手）艇釣 岸釣 <br />\n細魚多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名"},{"pid":"5c7f9cf701de4f5b3ae18dcd976f3f2a6ca56ffe","tid":203010,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"屯門釣 玩魚牌 最多有泥鯭"},{"pid":"0cc363b233ed52862a64892508e548bc8334ddf1","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"我釣開石九，牛鰍，火點，細鱗"},{"pid":"732c9864527c0f170328607e8c222db89a256fe5","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知那邊仲有「爛肉梳」釣？釣過一次好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7423f28934a3c7a45ff9d4fdedb90ad380aba96","tid":203010,"uid":27618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"玩開筏仔"},{"pid":"0a0d823fb632751b25e9e05244bea26fedc2d186","tid":203010,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家知唔知那邊仲有「爛肉梳」釣？釣過一次好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n青衣"},{"pid":"a2128ab7a3c260bddf190f18963431e0d110091c","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"將軍澳咩位多魚釣？"},{"pid":"b76845f78b03ef72b520817b33605c57384932d9","tid":203010,"uid":60178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f75b0f921c5011c37e14268e298f193a4fd74a","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常要，啲魚好醒令你卡石"},{"pid":"bc633d65071b17eeeb09d407c16b0babad171d0d","tid":203010,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"琴日將軍澳釣，全部魚毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112b8a8f0e67d403bf89f4c38ba5e48a203077a0","tid":203010,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"我釣左好多年魚。有咩唔明可以問我 <br />\n我既心得係。唔使買桿既 <br />\n<br />\n一個八磅魚排。一包鹇。一袋鉛。兩條蟲。一把刀。夠玩半日 <br />\n<br />\n首先執齊以上裝備。去七仔買半打藍妹。 <br />\n行過街市斬半隻燒鵝。 <br />\n<br />\n去就近碼頭霸個靚位。 <br />\n<br />\n隊罐啤食隻脾先 <br />\n<br />\nD骨就掉落海引d魚 <br />\n之後就開壇落鉛幫鹇。一條蟲切十份 <br />\n咁你就有廿份餌。 <br />\n之後就掉落海等。當然。過程中不忘隊啤食燒鵝同隔離d釣友吹水。吹得幾個字一扯！ <br />\n<br />\nOk kick石！ <br />\n<br />\n扯斷收返上黎又綁過。 <br />\n如是者十次八次用晒你d鉛同埋鹇之後。你d啤酒同燒鵝都所餘無幾（骨照舊掉落海引魚） <br />\n咁你就可以食埋隻鵝，飲埋罐藍妹，執埋d垃圾。有剩d蟲就比隔離or掉落海。 <br />\n之後拎返個冇左一半絲既魚排 <br />\n返去同屋企人講 <br />\n「刁。今日（落雨/冇落雨/大太陽/冇太陽）。成個海都冇魚 。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef5ab89cda564ea7dd994f858d0a74c6297bfd","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常要，啲魚好醒令你卡石</blockquote><br />\n咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a68654d7a9503330b9a0d388222ec271369c4f","tid":203010,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"新手完全唔撚識，細個跟過老豆用手排釣<br />\n想係避風塘，碼頭釣，應該買咩竿好？"},{"pid":"871c47e1c21b4a4527474664eccc9c54e1132401","tid":203010,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常要，啲魚好醒令你卡石</blockquote><br />\n咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過比手掌大嘅梳囉仔 頂著成15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為係石狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：岸釣 新手前打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06f8804cdb013c4e6c320b7943a2439fa04a809","tid":203010,"uid":19101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"住大澳，係大澳同東涌啲碼頭位釣<br />\n依期冇咩魚釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383bab35ef8699b8ebc9fe27187903d567c518cc","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"我見條條都好過癮咁<br />\n諗住暑假去玩次<br />\n有冇師兄試過<br />\nimg]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c5e2f06d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg[/img]</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_4219ac3fb33ebeee9fb6af42f36d0196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F162639_4219ac3fb33ebeee9fb6af42f36d0196.jpg&h=4f259657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68ba93ddfec6653549105189fc5259f364f8bef4","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見條條都好過癮咁<br />\n諗住暑假去玩次<br />\n有冇師兄試過<br />\n[/img][url]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg[/img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e64ca11b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_89fe2470075403b555b3396eee1265e3.jpg[/img][/url]</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/162639_4219ac3fb33ebeee9fb6af42f36d0196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F162639_4219ac3fb33ebeee9fb6af42f36d0196.jpg&h=4f259657&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66U5HRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66U5HRj.jpg&h=cc31d1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2c52f542b606f98edfe13507ebf4e3dc4915755","tid":203010,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常要，啲魚好醒令你卡石</blockquote><br />\n咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 係分投釣(沉底) 定磯釣(浮波)<br />\n磯釣都會kick 石, 但視乎你釣幾深, 你set高釣水面魚當然唔會kick石啦"},{"pid":"29217e9e5fbd92581d1a0d78701c064e817ea129","tid":203010,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"巴絲其實一開波點學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39df5cf13cf8009a0c9a778e6f08304cf36fbb4c","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岸釣係咪一定要綁浮標/波？事關我經常卡石卡到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常要，啲魚好醒令你卡石</blockquote><br />\n咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 係分投釣(沉底) 定磯釣(浮波)<br />\n磯釣都會kick 石, 但視乎你釣幾深, 你set高釣水面魚當然唔會kick石啦</blockquote><br />\n如果要釣沉底魚嘅話，有啲咩方法可以減少kick 石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  釣一晚差唔多kick 成十幾次 （手線碼頭釣）"},{"pid":"56862f3ea8bd9a432b1123afe10a8dee80c1af46","tid":203010,"uid":74037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴絲其實一開波點學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老豆教，係艇仔釣，所以淨係識玩手釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a686e3065c6944b3269789df90f32d086a1da6ac","tid":203010,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴絲其實一開波點學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前無上網<br />\n問隔離阿叔最實際 <br />\n<br />\n新手最忌 <br />\n1. 魚勾太大 <br />\n2. 唔識打結"}]}